parameters.text:
=Using the following inputs, generate banner text in standard marketing hierarchy:

Post Goal: {{ $('Edit Fields2').item.json['Post Goal'] }}
Main Hook:{{ $('Edit Fields2').item.json['Main Hook'] }}
Core Message: {{ $('Edit Fields2').item.json['Core Message'] }}
Key Features: {{ $('Edit Fields2').item.json['Key Features'] }}
Benefit:{{ $('Edit Fields2').item.json['Benefit (optinal)'] }}
